release_note: Happy Holidays! We re excited to share some exciting updates. We ve redesigned our app icon to make it feel more aligned with our brand. We made some performance improvements to resolve a lag issue with our journaling flow. We added a prompt for reviews so we can know how you feel about our app. We removed the prompt text at the end of the journal cycle for uninterpreted reflection. Added additional lines in the journal feed so you can see more of your content.
